com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger.features

Class PosTaggerFeatureParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.machineLearning.features.AbstractFeatureParser<PosTaggerContext>
      • com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger.features.PosTaggerFeatureParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureClassContainer, FeatureParser<PosTaggerContext>, FeatureParserInternal<PosTaggerContext>

    public class PosTaggerFeatureParser
extends AbstractFeatureParser<PosTaggerContext>
    The central class for parsing a descriptor containing pos-tagger features.
    The list of available features is given in addFeatureClasses(FeatureClassContainer).
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
